      <name>Dell OpenManage Enterprise by HTTP agent</name>
      <description>Dell OME API monitoring template v2.0 FULL. Auto-discovery, Status/Power/Temperature/Health, Inventory (CPU/Memory/Disk/RAID/PSU/Fans/Network), Power Metrics (Instant/Avg/Max), Utilization (CPU/Memory/IO), GPU, Alerts, Session control.</description>
